comments.body:
@muzixing sorry for the delay, had some other work to address.  I addressed (and resolved) all comments that do not warrant further discussion.  Mainly I reverted my changes back to the OLD versions as requested. 

The two remaining unresolved comments may warrant review, but I feel like the changes are ready to be merged at your convenience (happy to address any further comments of course). 

P.S. I will hold off on further merge requests due to the WGLC.
